{"tid":1188411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"約旦公開拋售中國新型無人機","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T10:24:07.000Z","uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d2752ec16f060714ae39f2d3ed80d204af1cdc","tid":1188411,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://idrw.org/disappointed-with-chinese-uavs-jordan-puts-them-on-sale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fidrw.org%2Fdisappointed-with-chinese-uavs-jordan-puts-them-on-sale%2F&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=eb73dae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://idrw.org/disappointed-with-chinese-uavs-jordan-puts-them-on-sale/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QF7E8EN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQF7E8EN.jpg&h=29f3b568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點內容<br />\n<br />\nCH-4B係中國製既無人機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，兩年前約旦由中國入手，但空軍對其表現極度失望及不滿，於是響6月3日公開拋售<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">However, its six CH-4B UAVs were reportedly delivered about two years ago. The RCAF told Shepard Media in November 2018 it was not happy with the aircraft&rsquo;s performance and was looking to retire them</span>. <span style=\"color: red;\">CASC has been accused of copying the design of General Atomics Aeronautical Systems&rsquo; MQ-9 Reaper UAV, due to the CH-4B&rsquo;s close resemblanc</span>e. <br />\n<br />\nNonetheless, many countries in the Middle East have chosen to buy what critics call &ldquo;knock-off&rdquo; Chinese UAVs because the Missile Technology Control Regime restricts the USA to exporting its large, fast-moving UAVs to only its closest allies."},{"pid":"8f7b52e53f1b915822f81d8f0177053c4032d639","tid":1188411,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:08:54.000Z","msg":